Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭從未結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯盟宇宙軍以及拉爾康帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都假設戰爭將會來臨而開始備戰的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續創下歷史性勝利的驅逐艦微風號的乘員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接獲軍司令部之命到地上執勤兼度假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的休憩時間流逝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會下雨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.45,0:00:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老是下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.22,0:00:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都糟蹋掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我特別吹的髮型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，由理子．史塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，參謀部長室?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.28,0:01:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳直接看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.69,0:01:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.76,0:01:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在邊境空域單獨航行中的運輸船團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.40,0:01:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連絡突然中斷，從雷達上消失之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.57,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻請求緊急救援，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.42,0:01:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒發現任何生存者\N後來事故調查書上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.16,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷是意外，仍繼續調查原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.11,0:02:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們情報局認為\N在斷定為事故之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有別於調查總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.47,0:02:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做再度調查，看有沒有別的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.97,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時有發現拉爾康戰機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達網上，沒有發現敵機的行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是說有並非意外的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為不知道，才要請妳調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.65,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻著手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在情報分析室\N為妳準備一張桌子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.36,0:02:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨過晴天 (1)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.67,0:02:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，哪有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是工作嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.21,0:02:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得最近打好幾通電話到妳房間\N都找不到人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，每晚都加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.08,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這次調到地方執勤\N一半是來放假耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意是要我們放鬆，不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，事故的背後\N會是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.83,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經不行了，每次都以任務為重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還說"是"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎，不是還有時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.61,0:03:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是提出報告的日子，對不起\N那，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個工作狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔少校，有妳的包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.70,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我訂的?\N這一定是哪裡搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢也付過了?怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有訂啞鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.39,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，前天晚上也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼怪風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，喂喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呀，真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金姆中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是怎麼了，剛才怎麼突然掛斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.04,0:07:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妳?這是第一通?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對，那就後天午休的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小包裹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近怎麼怪事連連呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.86,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是找不到調查總部判斷外的要因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，這樣就完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.48,0:08:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，反正收都收了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，我可能真的工作過度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山、山本上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才要回去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想回去，剛好看到少校妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了不少酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會嚇到妳，實在很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.36,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那樣的\N我覺得自己好像被人跟蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.71,0:10:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我是說"覺得"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.12,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，那就讓我負責送妳到家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我家就在附近\N沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，啞鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計程車，計程車計程車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M67
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.21,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎，就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.04,0:12:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面到底裝什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.43,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了妳，特別把工具室做些改裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.77,0:13:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理子．史塔少校\N隸屬行星聯盟宇宙軍情報局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.11,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在負責邊境空域的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳每晚工作到很晚，一定很累吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們跟蹤我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打無聲電話給我，然後送奇怪的東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候真的失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙，放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾康人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們目的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.65,0:14:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，跟謠傳的一樣\N很好強的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不必急，現在就解釋給妳聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔少校，我一定救妳出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重寫報告書?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請少校在報告書上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.78,0:14:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上拉爾康新武器的機密情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.92,0:14:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及運輸船事故的調查結論\N就說，推斷事故可能是拉爾康的襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾康的新武器?那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且那地方，一艘拉爾康軍艦都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連戰機也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不要妳寫事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查總部斷定是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.91,0:15:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查原因的時候\N情報局提出反駁的主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說，藉著擾亂情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使行星聯盟軍陷入混亂\N是我們的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外再製造與聯盟宇宙軍的敵對意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校的判斷，將會成為軍方的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.94,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個手續很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，只要上了資料鎖\N妳就無法修改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.85,0:15:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳想修改\N這裡面的機密情報與程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會自動放出病毒感染主電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做不只是擾亂情報局的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.56,0:15:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會使軍方全體功能痲痺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的不是痲痺情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是想辦法點起戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該往左往右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是往中央走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能做到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼只有妳知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好出人意料的是妳的生日數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不認為妳會乖乖聽從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.92,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是泰勒艦長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.46,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很有興趣想知道\N他的運氣會好到什麼程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是安裝在\N泰勒艦長自宅的炸彈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈的遙控起爆開關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳很難相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.85,0:17:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們借用一下監視器的線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾稍微修改一下，是可以使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.37,0:17:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是車輛課\N這次是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是艦長的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳相信了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.44,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果泰勒艦長不在家\N那麼就證明了他是個運氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果他在家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.12,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，請決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校畢竟是個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以軍人的身份來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.29,0:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長是軍方不可或缺得重要人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.03,0:19:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.88,0:19:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有腳步聲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.51,0:19:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在附近打轉，聽了就發毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要是接近這裡，就格殺勿論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.73,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們那麼想打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.20,0:19:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打仗是拉爾康帝國的歷史\N我們的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.07,0:19:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要聊沒意義的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球的人只會吃喝拉睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說戲言了，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩中央這條路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M67
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.86,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水門?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門?就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水門打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離水流到達還有40秒\N請快點避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.00,0:22:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.37,0:22:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.61,0:22:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.98,0:22:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.05,0:22:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.96,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.93,0:23:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙，居然耍這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.77,0:23:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，出口在反方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.24,0:23:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊靠近水門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.47,0:23:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到蓄水區的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.01,0:23:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.98,0:23:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.86,0:23:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.15,0:23:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵欄杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.55,0:23:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.99,0:24:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，出口旁邊有梯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.08,0:24:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.61,0:24:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.05,0:24:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.20,0:24:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.73,0:24:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.20,0:24:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.81,0:25:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，少校快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.11,0:25:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.40,0:26:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.41,0:26:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.01,0:26:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們竟然裝了那麼危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.65,0:26:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的功勞，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.72,0:26:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你來，事情不知會變成怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.46,0:26:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，如果我有送妳回家的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.73,0:26:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我不夠注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.93,0:26:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該去拿這東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.43,0:26:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西!?這不是妳重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.40,0:26:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，還讓你那麼費心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.91,0:26:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.41,0:26:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啞鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.78,0:26:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啞鈴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.41,0:26:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉爾康人送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.42,0:26:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位這麼早到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.05,0:26:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.12,0:26:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，你們剛剛慢跑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.66,0:27:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，我跟史塔少校\N哪有那個閒情逸致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.00,0:27:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，由理子\N我想拜託妳一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.53,0:27:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我郵購了東西，請他們送到妳的桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.04,0:27:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有收到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.81,0:27:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是郵購啞鈴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.04,0:27:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，已經收到啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.55,0:27:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個，這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.05,0:27:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在我肚子前面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.25,0:27:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有收到怎麼不早說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.76,0:27:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.09,0:27:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.96,0:27:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這樣按的吧
